<surface xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" ulx="0"
  uly="0" lrx="5406" lry="7052" xml:id="ox-ms_shelley_e3-0070" partOf="#ox-ms_shelley_e3" mith:folio="34v" mith:shelfmark="MS. Shelley e. 1">
  <graphic url="http://shelleygodwinarchive.org/images/ox/ox-ms_shelley_e3-0070.jp2"/>
  <zone type="main">
    <line>I saw two azure halcyons clinging downward</line>
    <line><mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">a</del>
        <add place="intralinear">A</add>
      </mod>nd thinning one bright <milestone unit="tei:seg" spanTo="#e3-0070.07"
        xml:id="e3-0070.09"/>mass<anchor xml:id="e3-0070.07"/>
      <add place="superlinear"><milestone unit="tei:seg" spanTo="#e3-0070.08" xml:id="e3-0070.10"
          />bunch<anchor xml:id="e3-0070.08"/></add> of amber berries <alt
        target="#e3-0070.09 #e3-0070.10" mode="excl" weights="0 1"/></line>
    <line>With quick long beaks, &amp; in the deep there lay</line>
    <line>Those lovely forms imaged as in a sky&#8212;</line>
    <line>So with my thoughts full of these happy changes</line>
    <line>We meet again, the happiest change of all. &#60;</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:stage" spanTo="#e3-0070.01"/>
    <line rend="right">Enter, the Spirit of the Hour</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e3-0070.01"/>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e3-0070.02"/>
    <line rend="center">Prometheus</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e3-0070.02"/>
    <line>We feel what thou hast heard &amp; seen&#8212;yet speak</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e3-0070.03"/>
    <line rend="center">Spirit</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e3-0070.03"/>
    <line>Soon as the <del rend="strikethrough">thu</del> sound had ceased whose thunder <add place="sublinear">filled</add></line>
    <line>The abysses <add place="sublinear"><metamark function="insert">^</metamark></add><add
        place="superlinear">of</add> the <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">air</del>
        <add place="superlinear">skies</add>
        </mod>, &amp; the wide earth; <space dim="horizontal" unit="chars" extent="5"/><add><metamark function="count">410</metamark></add></line>
    <line>There was a change...the impalpable thin air</line>
    <line><del rend="strikethrough">The light</del> And the all-circling sunlight were <add place="sublinear">transformed</add></line>
    <line>As if the sense of love dissolved in them</line>
    <line>And folded itself round the sphered world.</line>
    <line>My vision then grew clear &amp; I could see</line>
    <line>Into the mysteries of the Universe</line>
    <line>Dizzy as with delight I floated down</line>
    <line>Winnowing the lightsome air with languid <add place="sublinear">plumes</add></line>
    <line>My coursers sought their <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">pastures</del>
        <add place="superlinear">birthplace</add>
      </mod> in the sun</line>
    <line rend="indent5"><add><metamark function="count">401 </metamark><space dim="horizontal" unit="chars" extent="3"/><metamark function="count"
          >1778</metamark></add></line>
  </zone>
